I recently interviewed a CIO of a $25 billion company who told me his top two priorities currently are identifying:

text:
When you’re making a decision, an investment, prioritizing, or hiring someone: Are you looking at data at all? 

Many executives still rely on experience, but increasingly data will be influencing decisions and making big decisions smaller, says @nyike #CIOChatLive
